title: Yevgeni Kashentsev
text:
Yevgeni Nikolayevich Kashentsev (; born 12 March 1971) is a retired <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er. He also holds <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n citizenship.
He is the older brother of <a href="Nikolai%20Kashentsev">Nikolai Kashentsev</a>.
Honours.
Dinamo Minsk
Maccabi Tel Aviv
